<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <meta name="description" content="Premium modern website landing page" />
  <title>Northstar Premium</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #07111f;
      --bg-2: #0b1730;
      --card: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      --line: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      --text: #f8fbff;
      --muted: #aab7cf;
      --cyan: #7cecff;
      --violet: #8f6bff;
      --green: #56f0b3;
      --shadow: 0 30px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
      --radius: 28px;
      --max: 1220px;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      color: var(--text);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 15% 15%, rgba(124,236,255,0.14), transparent 0 26%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 85% 10%, rgba(143,107,255,0.18), transparent 0 28%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 50% 85%, rgba(86,240,179,0.08), transparent 0 24%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg) 0%, var(--bg-2) 42%, var(--bg) 100%);
      min-height: 100vh;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
    img { max-width: 100%; display: block; }

    .wrap { width: min(var(--max), calc(100% - 32px)); margin: 0 auto; }
    .glass {
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }
    .pill {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 10px 16px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      color: var(--cyan);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.24em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 15px 22px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-weight: 700;
      transition: 0.25s ease;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 0%, #eafcff 100%);
      color: #06111f;
      box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(124,236,255,0.18);
    }
    .btn-primary:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); }
    .btn-secondary {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      border-color: var(--line);
      color: #fff;
    }
    .btn-secondary:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }

    header {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 50;
      background: rgba(7,17,31,0.72);
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    }
    .nav {
      min-height: 80px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 18px;
    }
    .brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 14px;
      font-weight: 800;
    }
    .brand-mark {
      width: 46px;
      height: 46px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(124,236,255,0.95), rgba(143,107,255,0.95));
      color: #06111f;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(124,236,255,0.22);
      font-size: 20px;
    }
    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 28px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: #fff; }
    .menu-btn {
      display: none;
      width: 48px;
      height: 48px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 20px;
    }

    .hero {
      position: relative;
      padding: 72px 0 42px;
    }
    .orbs::before,
    .orbs::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      border-radius: 999px;
      filter: blur(70px);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .orbs::before {
      width: 320px;
      height: 320px;
      left: -80px;
      top: 50px;
      background: rgba(124,236,255,0.18);
    }
    .orbs::after {
      width: 360px;
      height: 360px;
      right: -120px;
      top: 20px;
      background: rgba(143,107,255,0.20);
    }
    .hero-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
      gap: 30px;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .hero h1 {
      margin: 24px 0 20px;
      font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6.7rem);
      line-height: 0.95;
      letter-spacing: -0.05em;
    }
    .gradient-text {
      background: linear-gradient(110deg, #fff 0%, var(--cyan) 40%, #b8a3ff 78%, #fff 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      background-clip: text;
      color: transparent;
    }
    .hero p {
      max-width: 720px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin: 0 0 30px;
    }
    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 34px;
    }
    .hero-card {
      padding: 18px;
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .hero-card-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 16px;
    }
    .metric {
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 24px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      min-height: 140px;
    }
    .metric strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 40px;
      line-height: 1;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .metric span {
      display: block;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.65;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    section { padding: 42px 0; }
    .section-head {
      max-width: 760px;
      margin-bottom: 26px;
    }
    .section-head h2 {
      margin: 18px 0 14px;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.8rem);
      line-height: 1.04;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    }
    .section-head p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.8;
      font-size: 17px;
    }

    .brand-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 14px;
      margin-top: 22px;
    }
    .brand-chip {
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 22px;
      text-align: center;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.72);
      font-size: 13px;
      letter-spacing: 0.28em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    }

    .cards-3,
    .cards-4,
    .cards-2 {
      display: grid;
      gap: 18px;
    }
    .cards-2 { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .cards-3 { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
    .cards-4 { grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); }

    .card {
      padding: 28px;
      border-radius: 28px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      transition: transform .25s ease, background .25s ease, border-color .25s ease;
    }
    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-4px);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
      border-color: rgba(124,236,255,0.24);
    }
    .card .kicker {
      color: var(--cyan);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.24em;
      display: inline-block;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .card h3 {
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      font-size: 24px;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }
    .card p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.75;
      font-size: 15px;
    }
    .list {
      padding: 0;
      list-style: none;
      margin: 18px 0 0;
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
    }
    .list li {
      padding: 12px 14px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .showcase {
      overflow: hidden;
      position: relative;
      padding: 0;
      border-radius: 34px;
    }
    .showcase-top {
      padding: 26px 26px 0;
    }
    .showcase-visual {
      padding: 26px;
      min-height: 290px;
      position: relative;
      background:
        linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.08), rgba(255,255,255,0.02)),
        radial-gradient(circle at 20% 20%, rgba(124,236,255,0.28), transparent 0 22%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 80% 20%, rgba(143,107,255,0.28), transparent 0 24%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.06), rgba(255,255,255,0.02));
    }
    .mock-window {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 28px 28px 28px 28px;
      border-radius: 28px;
      background: rgba(7,17,31,0.62);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .mock-bar {
      height: 48px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 0 16px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    }
    .dot { width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 999px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.24); }
    .mock-content {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr;
      gap: 18px;
      padding: 20px;
      height: calc(100% - 48px);
    }
    .mock-panel,
    .mock-stack > div {
      border-radius: 22px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    }
    .mock-panel {
      padding: 20px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .mock-line {
      height: 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.55), rgba(255,255,255,0.18));
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .mock-line.small { width: 42%; }
    .mock-line.med { width: 68%; }
    .mock-line.long { width: 100%; }
    .mock-graph {
      position: absolute;
      left: 20px;
      right: 20px;
      bottom: 20px;
      height: 110px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(124,236,255,0.16), rgba(124,236,255,0.03));
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .mock-graph::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 16px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 2px solid transparent;
      border-bottom-color: rgba(124,236,255,0.75);
      border-left-color: rgba(124,236,255,0.4);
      transform: skewX(-20deg) translateY(8px);
    }
    .mock-stack {
      display: grid;
      gap: 18px;
      grid-template-rows: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    }

    .process {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 0.9fr 1.1fr;
      gap: 18px;
      align-items: start;
    }
    .process-steps {
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .testimonial {
      min-height: 260px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }
    .testimonial blockquote {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 17px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.86);
      line-height: 1.8;
    }
    .person {
      padding-top: 18px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .pricing .card.highlight {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff 0%, #effcff 100%);
      color: #07111f;
      border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
    }
    .pricing .card.highlight p,
    .pricing .card.highlight .price-sub,
    .pricing .card.highlight li { color: rgba(7,17,31,0.72); }
    .price {
      font-size: 52px;
      line-height: 1;
      margin: 16px 0 10px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    }
    .price-sub {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .faq-item {
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    .faq-top {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 16px;
    }
    .faq-top h3 { margin: 0; font-size: 18px; }
    .faq-body {
      max-height: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: max-height .3s ease;
    }
    .faq-item.active .faq-body { max-height: 220px; }
    .faq-body p {
      margin: 14px 0 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.8;
      font-size: 15px;
    }
    .plus {
      width: 34px;
      height: 34px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      color: var(--cyan);
      flex: 0 0 auto;
    }

    .contact-box {
      padding: 34px;
      border-radius: 34px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 0.95fr;
      gap: 22px;
    }
    .form-grid {
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
    }
    .input, .textarea {
      width: 100%;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      color: #fff;
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 16px 18px;
      outline: none;
      font: inherit;
    }
    .textarea { min-height: 160px; resize: vertical; }
    .input::placeholder, .textarea::placeholder { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.38); }

    footer {
      padding: 30px 0 50px;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .reveal {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(24px);
      transition: opacity .7s ease, transform .7s ease;
    }
    .reveal.show {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }

    @media (max-width: 1100px) {
      .hero-grid,
      .process,
      .contact-box,
      .mock-content { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .cards-4 { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
      .cards-3 { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
      .brand-row { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    }

    @media (max-width: 760px) {
      .wrap { width: min(var(--max), calc(100% - 20px)); }
      .nav-links, .nav-cta { display: none; }
      .menu-btn { display: inline-grid; place-items: center; }
      .hero { padding-top: 34px; }
      .hero-card-grid,
      .cards-4,
      .cards-3,
      .cards-2,
      .brand-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .hero p, .section-head p { font-size: 16px; }
      .contact-box { padding: 24px; }
      .showcase-top, .showcase-visual { padding: 16px; }
      .mock-window { inset: 16px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="wrap nav">
      <a class="brand" href="#home">
        <div class="brand-mark">✦</div>
        <div>
          <div style="font-size:11px; letter-spacing:.28em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--cyan); font-weight:800;">Northstar</div>
          <div style="font-size:15px; font-weight:700;">Premium Studio</div>
        </div>
      </a>
      <nav class="nav-links">
        <a href="#services">Services</a>
        <a href="#work">Work</a>
        <a href="#process">Process</a>
        <a href="#pricing">Pricing</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
      </nav>
      <div class="nav-cta">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#contact">Book a Call</a>
      </div>
      <button class="menu-btn" id="menuBtn">☰</button>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main id="home">
    <section class="hero orbs">
      <div class="wrap hero-grid">
        <div class="reveal show">
          <div class="pill">Premium Website System</div>
          <h1>Make your brand feel <span class="gradient-text">expensive</span> the second people land.</h1>
          <p>
            This single-file landing page is built to look premium, modern, and professional out of the box.
            Paste it into your <strong>index.html</strong>, swap your text, and you have a polished site that works immediately.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#work">See the Showcase</a>
            <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#services">Explore Services</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="glass hero-card reveal">
          <div class="hero-card-grid">
            <div class="metric">
              <strong>212%</strong>
              <span>Average lift in perceived premium value across redesigned launches.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="metric">
              <strong>34d</strong>
              <span>To ship a modern polished first version when content is ready.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="metric">
              <strong>95+</strong>
              <span>Designed with clean structure so performance can stay strong.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="metric">
              <strong>AA</strong>
              <span>Readable contrast, strong spacing, and accessible hierarchy.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <div class="wrap reveal">
        <div class="pill">Trusted Aesthetic</div>
        <div class="brand-row">
          <div class="brand-chip">AETHER</div>
          <div class="brand-chip">VELORA</div>
          <div class="brand-chip">LUXEGRID</div>
          <div class="brand-chip">MONARCH</div>
          <div class="brand-chip">ORBITAL</div>
          <div class="brand-chip">NEXA</div>
          <div class="brand-chip">ATLAS</div>
          <div class="brand-chip">SUMMIT</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="services">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="section-head reveal">
          <div class="pill">Services</div>
          <h2>Everything you need to look premium without looking generic.</h2>
          <p>
            Replace these with your real offers. The layout is already designed for trust, clarity, and a modern wow factor.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="cards-3">
          <article class="card reveal">
            <div class="kicker">Strategy</div>
            <h3>Brand Positioning</h3>
            <p>Messaging, offer framing, and a value story that makes your business feel clear, credible, and worth more.</p>
            <ul class="list">
              <li>Audience clarity</li>
              <li>Offer architecture</li>
              <li>Messaging direction</li>
            </ul>
          </article>
          <article class="card reveal">
            <div class="kicker">Design</div>
            <h3>Premium UI / UX</h3>
            <p>Luxury-inspired layouts with cinematic spacing, refined typography, and elegant interactions that feel current.</p>
            <ul class="list">
              <li>Modern responsive layout</li>
              <li>High-end visual direction</li>
              <li>Conversion-focused structure</li>
            </ul>
          </article>
          <article class="card reveal">
            <div class="kicker">Development</div>
            <h3>Fast Front-End</h3>
            <p>Clean code, smooth behavior, and a single-file setup that is easy to paste, launch, and customize.</p>
            <ul class="list">
              <li>Single-file implementation</li>
              <li>Works without frameworks</li>
              <li>Easy to edit content</li>
            </ul>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="work">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="section-head reveal">
          <div class="pill">Showcase</div>
          <h2>A layout system built to impress in under five seconds.</h2>
          <p>
            Use this section for featured work, product screenshots, launches, portfolio highlights, or your main value proposition.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="glass showcase reveal">
          <div class="showcase-top">
            <div class="cards-3">
              <div class="card">
                <div class="kicker">Perception</div>
                <h3>Premium first impression</h3>
                <p>Strong hierarchy, dramatic spacing, glass surfaces, and gradient light create a polished modern feel.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="card">
                <div class="kicker">Clarity</div>
                <h3>Clean conversion flow</h3>
                <p>The page naturally guides attention from headline to proof to offer to contact with very little friction.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="card">
                <div class="kicker">Speed</div>
                <h3>Easy to deploy</h3>
                <p>You can paste this file as your index, replace the wording, and have a solid premium site today.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="showcase-visual">
            <div class="mock-window">
              <div class="mock-bar">
                <div class="dot"></div>
                <div class="dot"></div>
                <div class="dot"></div>
              </div>
              <div class="mock-content">
                <div class="mock-panel">
                  <div class="mock-line small"></div>
                  <div class="mock-line med"></div>
                  <div class="mock-line long"></div>
                  <div class="mock-line long"></div>
                  <div class="mock-graph"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="mock-stack">
                  <div></div>
                  <div></div>
                  <div></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="process">
      <div class="wrap process">
        <div class="section-head reveal">
          <div class="pill">Process</div>
          <h2>Sophisticated on the surface. Structured underneath.</h2>
          <p>
            This section gives you a clean way to explain your approach while keeping the visual presentation elevated.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="process-steps">
          <article class="card reveal"><div class="kicker">Step 01</div><h3>Clarify the message</h3><p>Define the promise, positioning, and strongest reasons someone should choose you.</p></article>
          <article class="card reveal"><div class="kicker">Step 02</div><h3>Design the impression</h3><p>Use strong typography, modern composition, and premium styling to increase perceived value.</p></article>
          <article class="card reveal"><div class="kicker">Step 03</div><h3>Guide the action</h3><p>Move visitors from curiosity to trust to inquiry with a smooth, intentional content flow.</p></article>
          <article class="card reveal"><div class="kicker">Step 04</div><h3>Launch and refine</h3><p>Swap in your real copy, contact details, and brand colors, then continue improving over time.</p></article>
        </div>
